RedGPU API v3.9.1-Alpha

RedGPU API / RedGPU / PostEffect / Vignetting

Class: Vignetting ​

Defined in: src/postEffect/effects/lens/vignetting/Vignetting.ts:28

Vignetting post-processing effect.

Creates an effect that darkens the edges of the screen to increase focus.

Can adjust size (range) and smoothness.

  • Example ​

typescript
const effect = new RedGPU.PostEffect.Vignetting(redGPUContext);
effect.size = 0.6;        // 비네팅 범위
effect.smoothness = 0.3;  // 경계 부드러움
view.postEffectManager.addEffect(effect);

Extends ​

  • ASinglePassPostEffect
